LIBFLIAPI FLIFlushRow

(flidev_t dev, long rows, long repeat)

Flush rows of a given camera.

Documentation

Flush rows of a given camera. This function flushes rows rows of camera dev repeat times.
Parameters:
dev - Camera to flush rows of.
rows - Number of rows to flush.
repeat - Number of times to flush each row.
Returns:
Zero on success.
Non-zero on failure.
See Also:
FLISetNFlushes
